Purpose:
Test whether the machine halt properly when the last process exit.

Usage:
-x shCXR.coff

Author:
Yue Chen

History:
2010-1-5 Yue Chen: The first version.

Note:
Copy all the files in userprog/test/test_exit to your test directory, DO NOT modify sample.sh and run your program
If the program runs correctly, it will NOT output any message and machine will halt.
Otherwise your program may not end or you may encounter other errors.
